<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Chomsky: By Focusing on Russia, We Ignore Trump’s Existential Threat to Climate</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
