<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-to-make-the-us-a-democracy-the-constitution-itself-must-change/" title="Noam Chomsky: To Make the US a Democracy, the Constitution Itself Must Change">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0724-donald-trump-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Donald trump speaks at a rally" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0724-donald-trump-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0724-donald-trump-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0724-donald-trump-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0724-donald-trump-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/2019_0724-donald-trump-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
